subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: In a match featuring 18 service breaks, Dinara Safina edged her fellow Russian Anastasia Pivovarova, 6-4, 2-6, 6-4, to reach the semifinals of the Grand Prix SAR in Fez, Morocco.
